reviews.text: Stop looking for something else and go here! This food is so good!  When you take a bite, walk away, then...look back at the food to ask "Why are you so...
Our group stopped in to check out North Market on our way to Hocking Hills from Detroit. We decided to give Willowbeez a try since it's something different...
Finally we're able to come to Willowbeez. Never had banana blossom before. Has the no fish banana blossom fry sandwich. Out of this world. Will have it...
